description:
This is a 35 minute workout called '30 Min ALL STANDING CARDIO ABS Workout | Lose Belly Fat, No Jumping, No Squats, No Repeat' from the channel Eleni Fit.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: This is a really effective standing abs workout and doesn't include jumps, squats or lunges. Remember to squeeze your muscle while exercising! Let's do this! #nojumpingworkout  #allstanding 

❀Full Body Workout
❀Time: 40 sec on/ 10 sec rest

Calorie Burn 250 - 300 Cal
Warm Up 00:00 - 03:12
Workout 03:12 - 31:35
Cool Down 31:35 - 34:57

*The number of calories you burn will vary from person to person depending on your body composition, workout intensity and also fitness level but this might serve as a guideline.
